data.description: Great Kennesaw Location in the highly desirable Cyrus Creek Subdivision. Beautifully maintained, open concept, pool & playground in neighborhood. Beautiful kitchen w/stained cabinets and black appliances! No carpet anywhere! Master has walk in closet & dual vanities, separate garden tub & shower. Secondary bedroom with ensuite bathroom. One car garage. Private patio with extra storage wand fenced in back yard. Close to KSU,NCG theatre, Swift Cantrell park, Lake Acworth & more! Near Major Hwys,41, I-75 &,575. Highly sought after school district! This is a wonderful community that is quiet and well taken care of!
